Docs.summary: Contains a collection of designer options. This class cannot be inherited.

remarks.format: ## Remarks The <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerOptionService.DesignerOptionCollection> class is a collection that contains other <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerOptionService.DesignerOptionCollection> objects. This forms a tree of options, with each branch of the tree having a name and a possible collection of properties. Each parent branch of the tree contains a union of the properties of all the child branches.
